<lb ed="I" n="0182b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0182b0101">聞夫開士弘教。至人崇道。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>嗟三界之危苦。悼□生之□□。將欲□□□□。□□舟樑。勢位同於
<lb ed="I" n="0182b02" type="honorific"/>脫屣。國城均於<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>棄唾。然則勇猛不息。非為獨善。感通<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>所□。利□塵沙。是故大覺乘時。慈悲一切。
<lb ed="I" n="0182b03" type="honorific"/>持智炬於昏境。擊法鼓於<note n="0182001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">䏊＝聾【史】</note><app n="0182001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">聾</lem><rdg wit="【原】">䏊</rdg></app>俗。迷<note n="0182002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30980"/>＝邪【史】</note><app n="0182002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邪</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30980"/></rdg></app>反正。黑暗<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>遷明。應物有期。世雄示滅。運神功於忍土。布靈
<lb ed="I" n="0182b04" type="honorific"/>迹於大千。雙樹嵐鞞之下。乃興妙塔。顯節涼臺之上。驗諸圖象。思崇真正。世有人焉。冥中見曉。
<lb ed="I" n="0182b05" type="honorific"/>復鍾□覺。太師錄尚書事彭城王。峰峻鍾山。枝華寶樹。心薀天璞。器孕<note n="0182003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30928"/>＝全【史】</note><app n="0182003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">全</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30928"/></rdg></app>才。懸明鏡以臨方。置
<lb ed="I" n="0182b06" type="honorific"/>歸墟而受物。多藝遺姬旦之能。樹德蔑劉蒼之善。天之所縱。不獨人中。化金練石之方。時為陋
<lb ed="I" n="0182b07" type="honorific"/>術外生。調微之義。仍謂蕨言。窮神逐變。探冥弘道。藻身法海。竦慮玄門。以皮肉為坏器。以性<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>命
<lb ed="I" n="0182b08" type="honorific"/>為畫水。得寶藏於身<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>中。識金珠於額上。曰者□<note n="0182004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB07321"/>＝驂【史】</note><app n="0182004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">驂</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB07321"/></rdg></app>北邁。作牧維城。屈跡行春風之恩。<note n="0182005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30771"/>＝局【史】</note><app n="0182005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">局</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30771"/></rdg></app>道為<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>秋
<lb ed="I" n="0182b09" type="honorific"/>駕之術。循□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>問邑。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>褰襜高<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>視。爰有勝地。宿置伽藍。南望呼沱。漢騎蹈冰之所。北臨易水。燕臣<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>行
<lb ed="I" n="0182b10" type="honorific"/>歌之蹤。界<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>山俠藪。躡野縈林。泄雲<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>濆雨。□珠□□。以茲博敞。寔栖靈聖。於是輟駕委心。慇懃至
<lb ed="I" n="0182b11" type="honorific"/>道。悵房廡之隳壞。恨欹闕之不工。爰慕五<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>王。放□□之法。乃懷三<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>劉。興鏤金之想。徘徊正念。意
<lb ed="I" n="0182b12" type="honorific"/>在於斯。及謁帝文□。入牽人寶。星<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>火數迴。攝心彌篤。□□家臣。逾存經紀。搜<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>素珉青碧之珍。伐
<lb ed="I" n="0182b13" type="honorific"/>貞松<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>文<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>梓之木。揆星<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>成則。測日為准。架室□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>雙林之下。構<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>尊像毗舍之地。龍王愧巧。天帝<note n="0182006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">慙＝慚【史】</note><app n="0182006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">慚</lem><rdg wit="【原】">慙</rdg></app>工。
<lb ed="I" n="0182b14" type="honorific"/>懸如意於暗中。不勞燈炬。置炎光於鍑下。自然香食。至如琢龍次<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>玉。摹立靈象。妙範合聖。奇相
<lb ed="I" n="0182b15" type="honorific"/>通神。光絕金膏。明兼銀燭。成就等應見之容。圓滿<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"/>若下生之<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>狀。□僧德眾。踵至如林。憑心正路。
<lb ed="I" n="0182b16" type="honorific"/>絕迹疑<note n="0182007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">䋄＝網【史】</note><app n="0182007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">網</lem><rdg wit="【原】">䋄</rdg></app>。持法鉤以牽毒。流智水以銷煩。戒行周圓。衿神空淨。圍繞晝夜。讚嘆頂禮。香氣如臺。
<lb ed="I" n="0182b17" type="honorific"/>花浮成蓋。風林搖薄。生微妙之音。蓮<note n="0182008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30981"/>＝沼【史】</note><app n="0182008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">沼</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30981"/></rdg></app>環迴。發哀雅之韻。翻同天上駕御之<note n="0182009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31168"/>＝園【史】</note><app n="0182009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">園</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31168"/></rdg></app>。鬱似人間花林
<lb ed="I" n="0182b18" type="honorific"/>之窟。資父事君。奉<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>國遺己。宣茲願力。上奉　皇家世祀。共圓□周。久隆基興。方地齊固。乘寶殿
<lb ed="I" n="0182b19" type="honorific"/>以飛空。駕金輪而傍轉。珠囊不委。玉鏡恒暉。蠢蠢□生。咸歸□覺。若夫一念小善。猶居忉利之
<lb ed="I" n="0182b20" type="honorific"/>上。兩錢輕拖。仍成羅漢之果。況乃據<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>憂之土。立大乘之宅。業深金剛之海。功□□玉之山。歸
<lb ed="I" n="0182b21" type="honorific"/>生生之福。出死死之苦。永銷煩惚。畢竟清涼。勒茲琬琰。弘此偈讚。其詞曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0182b22" type="honorific"/>迷路遙緬。欲境<note n="0182010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30983"/>＝遼【史】</note><app n="0182010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遼</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30983"/></rdg></app>闊。輪轉無窮。環循不脫。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>性猶狂<note n="0182011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𤉢＝象【史】</note><app n="0182011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">象</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𤉢</rdg></app>。命同聚沫。毒箭傍侵。風刀下割。無名至道。
<lb ed="I" n="0182b23" type="honorific"/>權應時來。一音所說。万路咸開。人天迴向。魔梵俱摧。永懷寂滅。言昇妙臺。棺踊金色。林成鵠變。
<lb ed="I" n="0182b24" type="honorific"/><note n="0182012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30988"/>＝寶【史】</note><app n="0182012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寶</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30988"/></rdg></app>聚常湛。三乘東轉。喆人合道。英猷獨扇。乃隆磬石。　皇心逾睠。時應刺舉。南面維蕃。相彼□
<lb ed="I" n="0182b25" type="honorific"/>地。竦意祗<app type="star" corresp="#0182009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">園</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31168"/></rdg></app>。雕<note n="0182013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𡒅＝墻【史】</note><app n="0182013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">墻</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𡒅</rdg></app>通閣。繡柱朱門。高堂夏冷。幽室冬溫。爰圖色象。瑩磨成質。形類金山。項猶<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>朝
<lb ed="I" n="0182b26" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>日。<note n="0182014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30985"/>＝思【史】</note><app n="0182014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">思</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30985"/></rdg></app>極神造。妙窮化術。真謂飛來。全同涌出。珊瑚為蓋。琉璃作<app type="star" corresp="#0182007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">網</lem><rdg wit="【原】">䋄</rdg></app>。寶鑷搖音。靈鍾震響。樹名□
<lb ed="I" n="0182b27" type="honorific"/>脫。花稱<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>想。或鄣長袪。法門遂廣。磬此誓願。　皇道重明。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>法鼓恒韻。神鼎不輕。官府万國。朝□
<lb ed="I" n="0182b28" type="honorific"/>□靈。勒茲不朽。蘭菊其馨。　大齊太寧二年歲次壬午二月辛丑朔八日戊申。造訖故記之。
<lb ed="I" n="0182b29" type="honorific"/>僕射魏收造文　元建造寺主齊輔□兒侄等　碑主安<note n="0182015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𢝫＝喜【史】</note><app n="0182015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">喜</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𢝫</rdg></app>堤<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>陽人小字劉永長名<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"/>選</p>
</cb:div>
